data.description: 3/2 single-family home, located in the peaceful and family oriented neighborhood in Pompano Beach. Less than a mile from North Broward Hospital and major highways. This home features brand paver circular driveway, brand new hurricane impact windows and a newer roof. No HOA. Low property tax. This one will not last! Seller is motivated.
